{"tid":1577552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人，幫手留意所有失踪人口消息","createTime":"2019-09-17T18:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T03:25:20.000Z","uid":93479,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"49b67f8621053c21678040ac05752e11e613cd91","tid":1577552,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T18:16:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我知每曰發生好多事，好多post<br />\n<br />\n但唔可以再畀任何一單失蹤人口石沉大海<br />\n<br />\n最後只會變成無聲無可疑的被自殺案！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\n9月頭10日已經有28人自殺！時間仲要大部份係清晨，自殺無巨響，灣仔分屍死地下無血<br />\n劏房綁手膠袋笠頭無可疑，北角綁磚自殺無可疑<br />\n山邊清晨發現吊頸<br />\n秀茂坪自殺案！！<br />\nPOLY 出現IVE學生去偏遠地方跳樓！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"1e8a311f3470faf19feeb8eb7cce8c35aeee03ca","tid":1577552,"uid":93479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T18:19:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zu7Qbuk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZu7Qbuk.jpg&h=3c7f591c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又有<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇其他讀者見過該名男童<br />\n消息指佢於15號失蹤 警方亦都話搵唔到。<br />\n<br />\n有讀者於16號早上<br />\n在屯門醫院康復大樓電梯裏見到該名男童被兩名軍裝上了手扣。  <br />\n<br />\n讀者表示印象深刻 因為正常該時段 少見這類年齡出現 以及被上手扣 <br />\n當時男童身穿白色長袍 冇表面傷痕<br />\n<br />\n如有消息請pm @pinkwardd"},{"pid":"2a1b1ce5f9afb6a98e7b77ffc97045a063564214","tid":1577552,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T18:21:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dAeCAWD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdAeCAWD.jpg&h=95131404&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7769f90ab993376de4cc4d9609cabf895ad40de","tid":1577552,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T18:21:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oN1A63n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoN1A6